article_title: Pewaukee man dies in Vilas County snowmobile accident
article_text:
By of the

A 34-year-old Pewaukee man died Saturday afternoon when he fell off a snowmobile and was struck by a another snowmobile in Vilas County, according to the Sheriff's Department.

Jason Ringle was driving a snowmobile in Sayner when he fell off, was struck and died, according to a release from the Sheriff's Department.
